&lt;br/&gt;
//mycoreclass[@ID= &amp;#39;ArchNachl_class_003&amp;#39;]//label[@* = &amp;#39;A&amp;#39;]&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
I get a NullPointerException:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
